## Rules 
- every interface in domain mus export both the interface itself and the symbol for the interface
- symbol should be named `{InterfaceName}Symbol`
- if module implements created interface it should provide symbol not concreate implementatation 


## Example


### How to provide symbol

```
@Module({
  providers: [
    {
      provide: PKCEInterfaceSymbol,
      useClass: PKCEService,
    },
  ],
  exports: [PKCEInterfaceSymbol],
})
export class PKCEModule {}
```

### How to inject symbol
```
  constructor(
    @Inject(PasswordInterfaceSymbol)
    private readonly passwords: PasswordInterface,
    @Inject(PKCEInterfaceSymbol)
    private readonly pkce: PKCEInterface,
    @Inject(TokenPayloadInterfaceSymbol)
    private readonly tokenPayloads: TokenPayloadInterface,
  ) {}
```